<br>
As for places to train, you can either go up to a group and ask if you can practice your weapon skills on mobs they pull and they'll usually say it's ok, as long as you don't KS.  Otherwise, if you've got a great dmg group you can sometimes practice your skills in your own xp group, just make sure to ask your fellow group members if it's okay before you make the switch to a weapon you're not too good with. <p><center><IMG SRC=http://namsun.homestead.com/files/eqpics/namsunsig2.jpg><br>
